&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=caofangkun&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;caofangkun&quot;&gt;caofangkun&lt;/a&gt; IMHO, you can use &quot;grep -nC5 unzip ql/build.xml&quot; to look into the logic.&lt;br/&gt;
